y implemented using advanced silicon photonic processes, and the\nnumber of required optical fibers can be further reduced by using wavelength\ndivision multiplexing (WDM).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2022 20:29:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-31"}
