ent conditions for goal convergence. Finally, we provide\na challenging simulation scenario with multiple non-convex point cloud\nobstacles and demonstrate collision avoidance and goal convergence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2022 13:00:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-31"}
